title: Three Hospital Authority Members re-appointed
content_text: The Government announced today (April 7) the re-appointment of three members of the Hospital Authority. Mr Vincent Fang Kang and Mrs Gloria Ng Wong Yee-man had been re-appointed as members of the Hospital Authority for two years while Professor Lam Shiu-kum had been re-appointed for one year. The re-appointment took effect from April 1, 2004. The Hospital Authority now comprises a chairman, 20 non-official members, three public officers and one principal officer from the Hospital Authority.
